{"id":"54625b9a-e791-4a06-82f0-17c31b1e4a43","name":"Odysseus | EPIC The Musical","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"I suppose you'll be calling me captain from now on, eh?\"</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Abandoned by your family on a deserted island, due to your prophetic abilities, you find a group of men searching for food. Within a few minutes of discussion, it seems you've gained a father and 600 uncles.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⊹ ࣪ ﹏𓊝﹏𓂁﹏⊹ ࣪ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 48, 48);\"><strong>TW: Strong language.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">+</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">LONG intro!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Dear LORD! It was quite the struggle with this one haha But! So far the longest story of the series, nothing too extraordinary, <em>h o w e v e r, </em>I give you:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Sassy Polites.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yes, that is right.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Sassy Polites.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You are welcome for making him accurate and not a man-baby. Not on my watch!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">_________________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Epic The Musical Series Shortcuts:</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7e146bbe-3596-4f3c-9e60-2ca1a2a12caa_character-ares-epic-the-musical\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(188, 32, 32);\"><strong>× Ares | The Kin Of Wrath</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c616d9ea-f00a-403d-9a15-9036133364e5_character-poseidon-epic-the-musical\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 1